## Compare the four

### Array

* ordered
* changeable
* usually many values of the same type

### Tuple

* ordered
* fixed-position meaning
* often mixed types

### Object

* named properties
* best for describing one structured thing

### Set

* unique values only
* best for membership and deduplication

